{"tid":435320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過去3年  中國GDP年均增速7.2％","createTime":"2017-10-14T07:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T17:05:24.000Z","uid":141461,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6c44acb1c6ea372b80f47f5b3d9dbe2a3bae11","tid":435320,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"2017年10月14日 10:34 <br />\n<br />\n[本報訊]中國國家發改委副主任、國家統計局局長寧吉13日在國新辦新聞發佈會上表示，2013-2016年，國內生產總值年均增長7.2%，高於同期世界2.6%和發展中經濟體3%的平均增長水準，平均每年增量44413億元（按2015年不變價計算）。<br />\n<br />\n今年上半年，國民經濟運行穩中有進、穩中向好，國內生產總值同比增長6.9%，增速連續八個季度穩定在6.7%-6.9%的區間。"},{"pid":"459b03aa925a161c90b78dd44ffc0300a3234fd0","tid":435320,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"支那你話你10%都得嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a215c1fed95949ab7b0e09b8b3b5453634e51134","tid":435320,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3336756468f4518d507fddc9945698448c80ae02","tid":435320,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3177db857286edab6f73317aa679f0a01dce6a","tid":435320,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:40:04.000Z","msg":"每年都跌會唔會到有日變做負數?"},{"pid":"2309d5587f07c97bec9e9b056a737edb676d6a35","tid":435320,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"7.2%好少，加到200%才似共產黨作風！"},{"pid":"9f7a6baf05871dc428083e8ea372c0806333dfd4","tid":435320,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"反正都是老作！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ea69c41d150c9efb3d4ffcbeee84c2ee09380f","tid":435320,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:2